Afurika Tshipembe (South Africa) ndi shango li no wanala kha pida thsa tshipembe tsha dzhango la [[Afurika]]. Mashango are tsini nalo ndi [[Zimbagwe]], Namibia, Mozambikwi, Swazini (Swaziland), li-Sotho (Lesotho) na Vhu-Tswana.

Afurika Tshipembe li na divhazwakale khulwane.

Vhathu vha Afurika Tshipembe ndi vhathu vha u funa pfunzo. Hu na dzi univesithi dza fumbili-ina. Dzinwe dza hone ndi [[Univesithi ya Venda]] na [[Univesithi ya Johannesburg]].

